ttp_template:
<group name="user_pid_cpu_mem_vsz_rss_tty_stat_start_time_command">
{{USER}} {{PID | re("\\d+")}} {{CPU}} {{MEM}} {{VSZ}} {{RSS}} {{TTY | re(".*\\w.*")}} {{STAT}} {{START}} {{TIME}} {{COMMAND | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="stat_pid_cpu_mem_vsz_rss_tty_start_time_command">
{{U{{STAT}}ER}} {{PID | re("\\d+")}} {{CPU}} {{MEM}} {{VSZ}} {{RSS}} {{TTY | re(".*\\w.*")}} S {{START}} {{TIME}} {{COMMAND | ORPHRASE}}
</group>

textfsm_template:
Value USER (\S+)
Value PID (\d+)
Value CPU (\d+\.\d+)
Value MEM (\d+\.\d+)
Value VSZ (\d+)
Value RSS (\d+)
Value TTY (\S+)
Value STAT (\S+)
Value START (\d+|\?|<|\[\])
Value TIME (\d+\:\d+)
Value COMMAND (.+)

Start
  ^\s*${USER}\s+${PID}\s+${CPU}\s+${MEM}\s+${VSZ}\s+${RSS}\s+${TTY}\s+${STAT}\s+${START}\s+${TIME}\s+${COMMAND} -> Record
